name: Jay-Tex Engineers
overview: Incepted in year 2001, we, “Jay-Tex Engineers”, are a trustworthy firm engaged in manufacturing and supplying a commendable Industrial Fountain, Outdoor Fountain & String Fountain. Under this elegant range, we offer Cascade In Row Fountain, Cascade Fountain, Garden Stone Fountain, Ascending & Descending Fountain, Three Foaming Fountain, Light Floating Outdoor Fountain, Floating Outdoor Fountain, Architectural Outdoor Fountain, Blue Led Outdoor Fountain, Round String Fountain, Dark Cladding String Fountain, Long String Fountain & Textile Machinery Parts. Based in Ahmedabad (Gujarat), India, since incorporation, ours is a Sole Proprietorship (Individual) firm. Our offered frosted films are known for their features like elegant designs, attractive looks and low maintenance.
